OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,FFamilies of those affected by the
OL,7,FHillsborough Disaster and the
OL,8,FManchester Arena attack met with Sir
OL,9,FKeir Starmer to call for assurances
OL,10,Fthe new law will apply in the fullest
OL,11,Fway to security services.
OL,13,FBut despite the hour-long meeting,
OL,14,Ffamilies said they were still
OL,15,Fdisappointed with the result and
OL,16,Fwithdrew their support, urging the
OL,17,Fprime minister to rethink before
OL,18,Fbringing it before parliament again.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
