OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,FCaroline Curry, who lost her son Liam,
OL,7,F19, in the Manchester Arena attack,
OL,8,Fsaid she was "disappointed, annoyed,
OL,9,Finfuriated, let down."
OL,11,F"It's given MI5 cart blanche to do
OL,12,Fwhat they want, say what they want and
OL,13,Fhide behind corporate witnesses and
OL,14,Fthat's not how it should be," she
OL,15,Fadded.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
