OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,F"Given that the carve out for the
OL,7,Fsecurity services has not been removed
OL,8,Fand that the head of the security
OL,9,Fservices in effect decides what
OL,10,Finformation can go to an inquiry or
OL,11,Finquest, this is not a law that
OL,12,Fsatisfies the Hillsborough families
OL,13,Fand at present they can't support it,"
OL,14,FElkan Abrahamson, of Hillsborough Law
OL,15,FNow, said.
OL,17,FWhen asked what happens next Mr
OL,18,FAbrahamson said it was "up to the PM"
OL,19,Fbut they had urged him "not to proceed
OL,20,Fon Monday and take some time to think
OL,21,Fabout things".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
