OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F393A1768504374
OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,F"Frankly if he hasn't got the guts to
OL,7,Fstand up to the security services it
OL,8,Fdoesn't matter how long he's going to
OL,9,Ftake we're not going to get to a
OL,10,Fposition where we're all in
OL,11,Fagreement," he added.
OL,13,FThe landmark law, officially known as
OL,14,Fthe Public Office Accountability Bill,
OL,15,Fwould mean public servants could face
OL,16,Fjail if they are found to have lied
OL,17,Fduring investigations or inquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
