OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,FBut its next, key stage through
OL,7,Fparliament was delayed after concerns
OL,8,Fwere raised that the "duty of candour"
OL,9,Fwas being watered down for security
OL,10,Fservices like MI5 and MI6.
OL,12,FCampaigners warned the draft version
OL,13,Fof the law, might allow intelligence
OL,14,Fchiefs to "hide serious failures
OL,15,Fbehind a vague claim of national
OL,16,Fsecurity".
