OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,FBut campaigners have pointed also to
OL,7,Fthe 2017 Manchester Arena bombing
OL,8,Fwhere they say MI5 was "able to
OL,9,Fpresent a false narrative to the
OL,10,Fpublic inquiry into the attack, not
OL,11,Fgiving a full picture of what they
OL,12,Fknew about the bomber", and say it
OL,13,Fmust never be allowed to happen again.
OL,15,FCaroline Curry and Lisa Rutherford
OL,16,Fjoined other families who lost loved
OL,17,Fones in the Manchester Arena attack
OL,18,Fand Hillsborough Law Now campaigners
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
