OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,FLisa Rutherford, whose 17-year-old
OL,7,Fdaughter Chloe was killed at the
OL,8,Fconcert alongside her boyfriend Liam
OL,9,FCurry, said she hopes Sir Keir puts
OL,10,Fhimself in their shoes.
OL,12,F"At the end of the day our kids were
OL,13,Fmurdered under this," she said.
OL,15,F"We're here to support Hillsborough
OL,16,FLaw for that reason. We've sat through
OL,17,Ftoday, we've got very involved in the
OL,18,Fdiscussions, I got quite personal and
OL,19,Ffrom my heart with Keir Starmer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
