OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,F"I think that if he can't take that
OL,7,Faway and think about it and put
OL,8,Fhimself in those shoes and realise
OL,9,Fthat all we want is the truth, because
OL,10,Fwithout the truth how can you fix
OL,11,Fanything, then I don't know what we
OL,12,Fdo."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
