OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,FResponding to Labour MP Anneliese
OL,7,FMidgley - who told the Commons MI5 had
OL,8,Fspent "six years misleading the public
OL,9,Fand concealing information" - Sir Keir
OL,10,Fsaid he had "always been clear the
OL,11,Fduty of candour applies to the
OL,12,Fintelligence services" and insisted
OL,13,Fproposed amendments to the Bill did
OL,14,Fnot water it down.
OL,16,FHe said: "It is right that there are
OL,17,Fessential safeguards in place to
OL,18,Fprotect national security, and we've
OL,19,Fgot that balance right."
