OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,FAmendments proposed by the Government
OL,7,Fon Wednesday brought spies within the
OL,8,Fscope of the legislation, subject to
OL,9,Fthe approval of the head of their
OL,10,Fservice.
OL,12,FMPs had been due to debate the
OL,13,FHillsborough Law on Wednesday, but the
OL,14,Fdiscussion was pushed back until
OL,15,FJanuary 19 to allow the Government to
OL,16,Fpropose changes that might address
OL,17,Fcampaigners' concerns.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
