OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,FLiverpool City Region Mayor, and
OL,7,FHillsborough Law campaigner, Steve
OL,8,FRotheram said: "It's got seismic
OL,9,Framifications and the government are
OL,10,Fvery clear that myself, Andy Burnham
OL,11,Fand the family's groups have told them
OL,12,Fthat it has to be the whole
OL,13,FHillsborough Law now and not part of
OL,14,Fit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
