OL,3,CHillsborough Law campaigners 'withdraw
OL,4,Csupport' for draft bill
OL,6,F"I think this is a reaction to the
OL,7,Famendments that the government wants
OL,8,Fto make which is that
OL,9,Forganisationally, MI5 and MI6 and all
OL,10,Fthe things around national security
OL,11,Fare included, so there's widespread
OL,12,Fagreement on that.
OL,14,F"This is about individual
OL,15,Fresponsibility of those people who
OL,16,Fwork for those organisations."
