OL,6,FThe law is named after the
OL,7,FHillsborough Disaster in 1989, which
OL,8,Fsaw 97 football fans unlawfully killed
OL,9,Fin a crush at the FA Cup semi-final,
OL,10,Fand subsequent efforts by some
OL,11,Fofficials to mislead about events that
OL,12,Fled up to the tragedy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
